# Production build env — committed on purpose.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* values are inlined into the client bundle and are public by design,
# so there is no secret here. This lets the deployed build reach the backend without
# any dashboard configuration. NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL is read at BUILD time (see
# src/lib/api.ts) — changing it requires a rebuild, not just a restart.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://leadpilot-backend-perc.onrender.com
